{"tid":2114404,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果在9月2日公佈，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊。","createTime":"2020-07-18T19:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:14:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"98a6b2efbc8de1d38b3401e4ce15a685a4bc7b0c","tid":2114404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:35:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/EGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FEGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=cd33c9e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FEGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4%2F&h=e75b14cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/EGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果在9月2日公佈，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊。</span><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷「爭取休息」：靠選民自主配票<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派初選結束，.................................<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公民黨林瑞華戰飲食界撼張宇人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M5AUL65xsFfgGMtnKQeeArZqTtk=/553x354/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEOSSJMDTY6EJRXPKWKXSGNHU4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM5AUL65xsFfgGMtnKQeeArZqTtk%3D%2F553x354%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEOSSJMDTY6EJRXPKWKXSGNHU4.gif&h=09223266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼區諾軒後，趙家賢亦宣佈退出35+協調工作；圖為民主派初選記者會。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢退出35+協調工作<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢昨發聲明。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n初選發起人戴耀廷於昨晚於facebook發帖，指隨着初選投票完成，各區都產生了出選隊伍，民主派35+初選協調主要工作已完成，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">而到選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果在9月2日，即選前4天公佈，一些區參選團隊會按民調結果停止選舉工程，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊，之後就要靠近二百萬名選民，「由所有人一起來完成這看似是不可能的任務」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n戴繼而指，作為民主派35+初選的協調者，到此階段餘下需要做的已不多，未來一段日子會爭取多一些休息時間，也可以更專注於學術的工作，但補充指不是甚麼也不做，「我必會與所有認同民主普選的香港人走在一起，在各自的位置，為達成這目標，繼續努力，直至民主普選臨到香港」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位初選牽頭人、........................................"},{"pid":"f6b5583d1e6d0d04fbc5a94edafbbde2f65fe72a","tid":2114404,"uid":306337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T20:04:23.000Z","msg":"2日點配得切..."},{"pid":"eea27eb8154ba8a8c2f3ee928654dcba597800b5","tid":2114404,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T20:22:34.000Z","msg":"死硬<br />\nD死忠實打哂交"},{"pid":"9b4294c5d1b4566545baa9cf1bd4fa00b9e1a523","tid":2114404,"uid":55689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T21:55:58.000Z","msg":"民調會唔會推翻初選嘅名次？"},{"pid":"df88dcab03047149c37e606d255dddc29197d14a","tid":2114404,"uid":302834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6b5583d1e6d0d04fbc5a94edafbbde2f65fe72a","tid":2114404,"uid":306337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T20:04:23.000Z","msg":"2日點配得切..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T22:01:11.000Z","msg":"4日<br />\n9月6選"},{"pid":"a2b5f1ee720ccc7f9185bc3995484c547e0fd39b","tid":2114404,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T22:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1c566a1dafaf0f7c336ab77a5de70e6940a522","tid":2114404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷：到時候，大家只需聰明地把選票平均分配到各區的民主派候選名單 #社評<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108002</a>"},{"pid":"1050a4cabe3e7a00c67016a3371ef682f9503995","tid":2114404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷：到時候，大家只需聰明地把選票平均分配到各區的民主派候選名單 #社評<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108002\" dat